----
ROOT.xml in localhost
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TPUBmDD1PrE&t=52s

If you want to have a site available at http://myhost:8080/myTestContext, put the following in 
$Catalina_home$/conf/localhost/whateveryoulike.xml

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="ISO-8859-1" standalone="no"?>
    <Context deployOnStartup="true" docBase="C:\path\to\your\docBase\" path="/myTestContext" reloadable="false">
    <Manager pathname=""/>
</Context>

or http://tomcat.apache.org/tomcat-7.0-doc/config/context.html#Defining_a_context
